<p><span style="font-family: Liberation Serif, serif; font-size: 1em"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">--------------------</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Theodoros of Melanthos </span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Qualification</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: Master With Special Honors, General Transmutation and Scriptreading (Umbrios College of Arcane Engineering), ??? Ranked 8</span><sup><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">th</span></sup><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"> among the acolytes.</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Party</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: Inotian</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Height</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: 5'7</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Blood Type</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: B-</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Resistances</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: AMN</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Culinary Notes</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: Low-Carbohydrate diet</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">Role</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">: Honored Guest</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif"><br></span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif">--------------------</span></strong></span></p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Ptolema of Rheeds</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: Special Accolade in Field Surgery (Minos Surgical Academy), Special Accolade in Orthopedic Surgery (Minos Surgical Academy), General Certification (Old Yru Guild of Runecrafters) Ranked 10th among the acolytes.<br><strong>Party</strong>: Viraki<br><strong>Height</strong>: 5'6<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: A+<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: AMN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: Extra meat, please<br><strong>Role</strong>: Honored Guest<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Seth of Ikkuret</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: First Degree Graduate, Healing (Akhem Military Academy), Master with Special Honors, Biomancy and General Medicine (Tem-Aphat University) Ranked 5th among the acolytes.<br><strong>Party</strong>: Mekhian<br><strong>Height</strong>: 6'1<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: O+<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: AMN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: Tree nut allergy<br><strong>Role</strong>: Honored Guest<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Ophelia of the Glass Fields</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: No formal qualification (Member of the Sacred Pallattaku Convention of Biomancers, also accepted through special sponsorship) Ranked 7th among the acolytes.<br><strong>Party</strong>: Rhunbardic<br><strong>Height</strong>: 5'8<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: N/A<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: AN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: Pescatarian diet<br><strong>Role</strong>: Honored Guest<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Lilith of Eskhalon</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: Journeyman Artificer of Intelligence (Ba'Hon Temple of Golemancy) Master, Human Biology (Irenca University) Ranked 6th among the acolytes.<br><strong>Party</strong>: Ysaran<br><strong>Height</strong>: 4'2<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: A-<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: AMN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: Dislikes bulb vegetables, dislikes root vegetables, dislikes beans, dislikes rare meat, dislikes rice, all food must be finely cut<br><strong>Role</strong>: Honored Guest<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Bardiya of Tuon</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: Microartificing, Master (Tuon Institute for Arcane Study) Anima Script Reading and Artificing Dual Course, Master and 2nd Placement (Aurya Grand University) Ranked 9th among the acolytes.<br><strong>Party</strong>: Rhunbardic<br><strong>Height</strong>: 5'11<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: A-<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: MN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: No alcohol<br><strong>Role</strong>: Honored Guest<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Ezekiel of Ilaadbat<br>Qualification: </strong>Valedictorian Master, Neurology (Old Yru Academy of Medicine and Healing), Second Scepter of 1406 (Temple of the Magi), Special Order for Outstanding Arcane Civil Service (Old Yru Council). Ranked 2nd among the acolytes.<strong><br>Party: </strong>Ysaran<strong><br>Height: </strong>5'8<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>AB+<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>AMN<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>Dislikes onions, aldehyde sensitivity<strong><br>Role: </strong>Honored Guest<strong><br>--------------------<br></strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Jia Fang<br>Qualification: </strong>Doctorates for General Medicine, Public Health, Medical Science, Microbiology, Philosophy, History (Saoyu University), Recognized Grandmaster of Alchemy (Saoic Arcanocracy) Full Graduate with Outstanding Honors (International Transmundane Academy). Ranked 1st among the Acolytes.<strong><br>Party: </strong>Saoic<strong><br>Height: </strong>6'0<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>O+<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>AM(N)<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>No<strong><br>Role: </strong>Honored Guest<strong><br>--------------------</strong></p>
<p>--------------------<br><strong>Linos of Melanthos</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: Grandmaster of Transmutive Healing by Grand Alliance Accolade, First Chair Professor at the Altaian Institute for Arcane Transmutation and Synthesis<br><strong>Party</strong>: Inotian<br><strong>Height</strong>: 5'6<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: B-<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: AN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: Dislikes shellfish<br><strong>Role</strong>: Order Master<br>--------------------</p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Neferuaten of Amat</strong><br><strong>Qualification: </strong>Grand Alliance recognized founder of the school of Entropic Thanatomancy, Second Magi at the House of Resurrection, Arcane Advisor to the Mekhian High Council<br><strong>Party: </strong>Mekhian<br><strong>Height:</strong> 5'8<br><strong>Blood Type: </strong>B-<br><strong>Resistances: </strong>AMN<br><strong>Culinary Notes: </strong>Avoid salt, if possible<br><strong>Role: </strong>Order Master<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Durvasa of Wayal<br>Qualification: </strong>Senior Professor of Biomancy at the University of Pallataku, former Physician to the First Administrator, former Underseer of the Office of Arcane Oversight<strong><br>Party: </strong>Viraaki<strong><br>Height: </strong>5'9<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>A+<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>(A)(M)N<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>Dislikes red meat<strong><br>Role: </strong>Order Master<strong><br>--------------------<br></strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Zeno of Apocyrion<br>Qualification: </strong>Inotian League recognized founder of the discipline of Neuromany (discipline-status internationally disputed), Permanent Professor at the Temple of Magi, co-founder of Thalatte Medicines. Considered one the most significant living arcanists.<strong><br>Party: </strong>Inotian<strong><br>Height: </strong>6'1 (male), 5'4 (female)<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>N/A<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>MN<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>Nothing pre-prepared or cheap, dislikes Viraaki cuisine<strong><br>Role: </strong>Order Master<strong><br>--------------------<br></strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Amtu-Heddu-Anna<br>Qualification: </strong>Retired Mistress of the Guild of Runescribes, senior advisor in Transmundane Engineering to the Old Yru Convention<strong><br>Party: </strong>Ysaran<strong><br>Height: </strong>4'9 (originally 5'2)<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>B+<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>(A)N<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>Low fat and salt diet due to advanced age. See detailed notes in main kitchen.<strong><br>Role: </strong>Order Master<strong><br>--------------------<br></strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Hamilcar of Kane<br>Qualification: </strong>High Artificer at the Ba'Hon Temple of Golemancy, head of House Kane and of all associated business ventures<strong><br>Party: </strong>Ysaran<strong><br>Height: </strong>6'7<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>AB-<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>(M)N<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>N/A<strong><br>Role: </strong>Order Master<strong><br>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------</strong><br><strong>Sac'Nicte'Ic'Nal</strong><br><strong>Qualification</strong>: N/A<br><strong>Party</strong>: Lluateci<br><strong>Height</strong>: 5'10<br><strong>Blood Type</strong>: O-<br><strong>Resistances</strong>: AMN<br><strong>Culinary Notes</strong>: Small portions<br><strong>Role</strong>: Servant of the Conclave<br><strong>--------------------</strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Yantho'Ic'Thal<br>Qualification: </strong>N/A<strong><br>Party: </strong>Lluateci<strong><br>Height: </strong>5'3<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>AB+<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>AM<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>Egg allergy, dislikes peppers<strong><br>Role: </strong>Servant of the Conclave<strong><br>--------------------<br></strong></p>
<p><strong>--------------------<br>Mehit of Eskhalon<br>Qualification: </strong>N/A<strong><br>Party of Origin: </strong>Mekhian<strong><br>Height: </strong>5'9<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>A-<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>Unassessed<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>Gluten allergy<strong><br>Role: </strong>Guardian of Attendee<strong><br>--------------------</strong></p>
