<p><strong>--------------------<br>Samium of Ur-Ysar<br>Qualification: </strong>Grandmaster and Professor of Egomancy, Dorthedon Academy (defunct)<br>Party: Ysaran<strong><br>Height: </strong>6'0<strong><br>Blood Type: </strong>A-<strong><br>Resistances: </strong>N<strong><br>Culinary Notes: </strong>No solid food<strong>, </strong>dislikes spicy dishes<strong><br>Role: </strong>Order Patron and Medical Guest<strong><br>--------------------<br></strong></p>
